nodes.text: 10 Key Battles is an article featured in Star Wars Insider 133 by Titan Magazines. It was written by Jason Fry and Paul R. Urquhart to go along with The Essential Guide to Warfare. The article lists the top ten key battles to take place in Star Wars Legends, including the Battle of Yavin, the Battle of Endor, the Battle of Ebaq, the Battle of Uquine, the Battle of Geonosis, the Battle of Coruscant, the Battle of Malachor V, the Battle of Ruusan, the Battle of Bilbringi, and the Second Battle of Fondor.
